OL,5, Almost eight million people are        
OL,6, struggling to pay their bills as living
OL,7, costs surge, a watchdog has warned.    
OL,9,FThe Financial Conduct Authority (FCA)  
OL,10,Festimated that 7.8 million people in   
OL,11,Fthe UK currently find bills a "heavy   
OL,12,Fburden", up from 5.3 million in 2020.  
OL,14,FEnergy, food and fuel prices have risen
OL,15,Fsharply in the last six months in part 
OL,16,Fbecause of the Ukraine war.            
OL,18,FInflation - the rate at which prices   
OL,19,Frise - increased to 10.1% last month,  
OL,20,Freturning to a 40-year high.           
